  EffectDiscription_ENG: "\uFF1CDNA Digivolution: 0 from [Apollomon] + [Dianamon]\uFF1E\uFF1CSecurity
    Attack +1\uFF1E (This Digimon checks 1 additional security card)\uFF1CBlocker\uFF1E
    (At blocker timing, by suspending this Digimon, it becomes the attack target)[When
    Digivolving] [When Attacking] If DNA digivolving, trash any 8 digivolution cards
    from your opponent's Digimon. Then, delete 1 of their Digimon with as many or
    fewer digivolution cards as this Digimon.[All Turns] When this Digimon would
    leave the battle area by an opponent's effect, by trashing 2 same-level cards
    in this Digimon's digivolution cards, prevent it from leaving."
